    "summary": "The user, who is taking the anticoagulant warfarin, asks for advice on managing a headache. The assistant correctly identifies the danger of mixing NSAIDs (ibuprofen) with warfarin, suggests acetaminophen as a safer alternative, and repeatedly advises consulting a professional (doctor, pharmacist, or nurse line) before proceeding.",
